                <p style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: center;">
                    At <span style="color: green;">BinIt</span>, we believe that hassle-free waste disposal makes life easier, giving you more time for what truly matters. Imagine a cleaner Ontario
                    without the stress of managing your garbageâ€”just schedule a pickup and let us handle the rest!
                    <span style="color: green;">Effortless waste disposal for a cleaner Ontario!"</span>
                </p>

                <div class="parisvideo">
                    <img src="/Public/images/waste pics.png" width="400px" height="350px" alt="waste" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="secondcontainer">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; text-align: center;">Take Control of Your Environment</h2>
        <div class="best-container">
            <div class="plastics-container">
                <img src="/images/trash-bin-garbage-delete-rubbish-waste-64.webp" width="100px" alt="garbage truck" />
                <p style="font-weight: bold;">Select your waste category: Plastics & Containers (PET, Bottles) or Organic Waste (Food Scraps).</p>
            </div>

            <div class="food-waste-container">
                <img src="/images/garbage_truck.png" width="100px" alt="a" />
                <p style="font-weight: bold;">Request for waste pickup in any location.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="mixed-waste-container">
                <img src="/images/sign_up.png" width="100px" />
                <p style="font-weight: bold;">Register to pick up waste in your preferred area and help keep your community clean and sustainable.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="feature-container">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">Features of the Binit Web App</h2>
        <p style="text-align: center;">Optimizing waste management with cost-effective and efficient evacuation solutions.</p>

        <div class="container-icons">
            <div class="feature-icon">
                <img src="/images/gabage_can.png" width="50" height="50" alt="Garbage Can Icon">
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem;">Request Pickups</h3>
                <p>The Binit web application allows home residents to request waste pickups and enables servicemen to provide waste collection services seamlessly.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-icon">
                <img src="/images/request.png" width="50" height="50" alt="Request Icon">
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem;">Home Resident Benefits</h3>
                <p>As a subscribed resident, enjoy efficient, regularly scheduled waste pickups and a swift, personalized call service from the comfort of your home or office.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-icon">
                <img src="/images/trash-bin-garbage-delete-rubbish-waste-64.webp" width="50" height="50" alt="Waste Selection Icon">
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem;">Customizable Waste Disposal</h3>
                <p>Choose the type of waste you want to dispose of with scheduled pickups and flexible service options tailored to your needs.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-icon">
                <img src="/images/Customer_Care-64.webp" width="50" height="50" alt="Customer Service Icon">
                <h3 style="font-size: 1.8rem;">24/7 Customer Support</h3>
                <p>BinIt provides round-the-clock customer support to ensure you receive assistance whenever needed.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="accordion-section">
        <div class="offer-container">
            <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; text-align: center;">FAQ</h2>
            <div class="accordion-container">
                <h4>What is Binit?</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion2">
                <p>Binit is a web application designed to streamline waste management by allowing home residents to request waste pickups and enabling servicemen to provide collection services efficiently.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-container">
                <h4>How does Binit work?</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion2">
                <p>Residents subscribe to Binit, schedule waste pickups, and select the type of waste for disposal. Servicemen receive requests and handle waste collection accordingly.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-container">
                <h4>Who can use Binit?</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion2">
                <p>Binit is available to <span style="color: green;">home residents</span> for waste disposal requests and servicemen for waste collection services.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-container">
                <h4>Is Binit available in my area?</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion2">
                <p>Our services are currently available in [your service locations]. You can check availability by entering your address on our platform.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="footer">
        <div class="footer-2">
            <div class="footer-1">
                <a href="/" class="logo">
                    <img src="/images/logo_transparent.png" width="100px" height="100px" alt="Website Logo">
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-contact">
                <h4>Contact us</h4>
                <div class="contact-icons">
                    <i class="fa fa-map-marker" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size: 1.5rem;"></i>
                    <p> lorem parsium</p>
                    <i class="fa fa-phone" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size: 1.5rem;"></i>
                    <p>+234-890-987-000</p>
                    <i class="fa fa-envelope" aria-hidden="true" style="font-size: 1.5rem;"></i>
                    <p>lorem pasium@gmail.com</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-payment">
                <h4> Payment Gateway</h4>
                <div class="payment-icons">
                    <img src="/images/pay1.jpg" />
                    <img src="/images/pay2.jpg" />
                    <img src="/images/pay3.jpg" />
                    <img src="/images/pay4.jpg" />
                    <img src="/images/pay5.jpg" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

